SHORTCUT KEYS
Keys	    Action
N + B	    Add hotspot (room link)
M + E	    Move hotspot
N + E	    Change hotspot target room
S + R	    Place remote switch
M + R + B   Place Media Remote switch
M + D	    Exit / Cancel any mode
S + Y	    Sync Home Assistant devices
I + M + U	Create new scene (upload 360 image)
I + M + R	Manage scenes (rename / delete)
S + D	    Save design (download JSON)
L + D	    Load design
D + T       Delete hotspot or Remote button